# Target/victim datasets and trained model artifacts — EXTERNAL INPUTS, never source.
# A target's dataset is the system being EVALUATED, not Crucible code. Data is
# scoped to its victim and co-located with it: examples/targets/<victim>/{data,artifacts}/.
# We commit the fetch+train scripts and a checksum manifest, never the bytes.
# (CRUCIBLE_DATA_DIR can override paths; /data/ at root is supported but not the convention.)
examples/targets/*/data/
examples/targets/*/artifacts/
/data/
/artifacts/
*.lgb
*.csv
*.csv.gz
*.parquet

# Operator/agent throwaway scripts (run agents misused repo-root instead of session temp)
scratchpad/
